import React from "react"
import {View, Button, TextInput, ScrollView, StyleSheet} from "react-native"

const CreateUser = () => {
    return (
        <ScrollView>
            <View>
                <TextInput placeholder="Nome" />
            </View>

            <View>
                <TextInput placeholder="Email" />
            </View>

            <View>
                <TextInput placeholder="Telefone" />
            </View>


        </ScrollView>
    )
}

export default CreateUser
